kernel module build for one version will not work on another version.
------------------------------------------------------------------
kernel modules are stored @ /lib/modules/<kernel version>/kernel
kernel modules  that are to be loaded at boot can be mentioned in /etc/modules-load.d/modules.conf
blacklist <module name>
copy all the module to  /lib/modules/<kernel version>/kernel then run "depmode"
Then run modprobe <module name without .ko>
